item.title: 60 Minutes Music Career Consultation
item.dc:creator: Afaq
item.description: Unlock more than just music with our headphones! Enjoy a complimentary 60-minute music career consultation as you immerse yourself in your favorite tunes. Elevate your listening experience and discover added value beyond pure enjoyment.
item.content:encoded:
Experience Immersive Audio:
  • Boasting 50mm dynamic drivers, these headphones deliver immersive audio tailored to your vibe, ensuring an unmatched listening experience.
Over-Ear Comfort:
  • Crafted with an over-ear design, these headphones prioritize your comfort during extended listening sessions, allowing you to groove to your favorite tunes for hours on end.
Dynamic Sound Drivers:
  • Equipped with moving coil drivers, these headphones offer dynamic sound reproduction that elevates your music experience to new heights.
Impressive Specifications:
  • Driver Size: 50mm
  • Impedance: 32Ω
  • Sensitivity: 90dB±3dB
  • Frequency Response: 20Hz-20kHz
  • Battery Capacity: 500mAh
  • Playback Time: Up to 20 hours
  • Charging Time: 2.5 hours
  • Standby Time: Up to 180 hours
  • Bluetooth Version: V5.0
  • Bluetooth Range: 10 meters
  • Compatibility: Compatible with all Bluetooth devices
Quality Assurance:
  • Country of Origin: China
  • Net Quantity: 1 unit
  • Imported and Marketed by: Imagine Marketing Limited
Ergonomic Design:
  • Designed with your comfort in mind, these headphones feature an ergonomic design that ensures a snug fit for prolonged use.
Exclusive Music Consultation:
  • Enjoy a complimentary 60 minutes music career consultation while indulging in your favorite tunes, adding value beyond just listening pleasure.
